module.name: org.opencms.apollo.template.democontents
module.import-script:
writeProperty '/' 'Title' 'Demo Site' writeProperty '/' 'Description' 'The OpenCms demo, brought to you by Alkacon Software.' writeProperty '/' 'NavText' 'Overview' writeProperty '/' 'template' '/system/modules/org.opencms.apollo/templates/apollo-page.jsp' writeProperty '/' 'apollo.css.wrapper' 'bg-blue:Blue background|bg-red:Red background|bg-grey-light:Grey background|bl-red-2-solid:Red line left|bl-grey-2-solid:Grey line left' writeProperty '/' 'apollo.css.iconbox' 'service-block service-block-default:%(key.apollo.setting.cssclass.lightbox)|service-block service-block-red rounded-2x:%(key.apollo.setting.cssclass.redbox)' writeProperty '/' 'apollo.css.icon' 'info:%(key.apollo.setting.iconclass.info)|link:%(key.apollo.setting.iconclass.link)|external-link:%(key.apollo.setting.iconclass.linkexternal1)|external-link-square:%(key.apollo.setting.iconclass.linkexternal1)|download:%(key.apollo.setting.iconclass.download1)|cloud-download:%(key.apollo.setting.iconclass.download2)|file-text-o:%(key.apollo.setting.iconclass.document)|file-pdf-o:%(key.apollo.setting.iconclass.pdf)|folder-o:%(key.apollo.setting.iconclass.folder)|globe:%(key.apollo.setting.iconclass.globe)|arrow-right:%(key.apollo.setting.iconclass.arrow)|check:%(key.apollo.setting.iconclass.check)' writeProperty '/' 'apollo.title.prefix' 'OpenCms |'
createUser 'Author' 'password' 'Sample author user' addUserToGroup 'Author' 'Users' addUserToRole 'Author' 'ELEMENT_AUTHOR'
createUser 'Editor' 'password' 'Sample editor user' addUserToGroup 'Editor' 'Users' addUserToRole 'Editor' 'EDITOR'
createUser 'Gallator' 'password' 'Sample user who can edit categories and galleries' addUserToGroup 'Gallator' 'Users' addUserToRole 'Gallator' 'CATEGORY_EDITOR' addUserToRole 'Gallator' 'GALLERY_EDITOR'
createUser 'Demo' 'password' 'Sample user with workplace access permissions' addUserToGroup 'Demo' 'Users' addUserToRole 'Demo' 'WORKPLACE_USER'
createUser 'Templator' 'password' 'Sample user with template development permissions' addUserToGroup 'Templator' 'Users' addUserToRole 'Templator' 'DEVELOPER'
